<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA86">
<l>kārkkalanta mēṉiyāṉ kaikalanta vāḻiyāṉ</l>
<l>pārkkalanta valvayiṟṟāṉ pāmpaṇaiyāṉ cīrkalanta</l>
<l>coṉṉiṉaintu pōkkārēl cūḻviṉaiyi ṉāḻtuyarai</l>
<l>yeṉṉiṉaintu pōkkuvarip pōtu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who don’t go about thinking of words blended with excellence [such as]</l>
<l>“he with a body blended with cloud [colour], the one with a discus blended with [his] hand,</l>
<l>the one with a strong belly blended with the earth, the one on the snake bed”,</l>
<l>thinking of what will they go now into the deep sorrow of pervasive Karma?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
